Note that these are re-run logs using a different cluster than in the paper. The numbers and results are close.
The by-clause scrambled formula solving time degration changes from 256%(in paper) to 308%, which is a reasonable deviation given the randomness of permutation. The by-iteration degration is still 12%.
Logs of the additional scramble scaling experiment as suggest by R3 is not available due to server issue. They will be included before full version as long as other suggest experiments.